- Footer: [footer.php](mdc:app/views/shares/footer.php)

## CSS Framework
- Bootstrap 5 is loaded from CDN
- Font Awesome 6 for icons
- Google Fonts for typography
- Custom CSS is included for specific components

## Form Styling
- Bootstrap form classes for consistent styling
- Alert components for error and success messages
- Card components for form containers

## Navigation
- Bootstrap navbar component for main navigation
- Dropdown menu for user account options
- Responsive design with mobile menu toggle

## Best Practices
- Use Bootstrap grid system for layout
- Include appropriate ARIA attributes for accessibility
- Use consistent spacing and typography
- Implement responsive design patterns
- Use proper HTML5 semantic elements

